com.vector.cfg.gen.core.bswmdmodel

Interface GIContainer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    GIHasContainer, GIHasParameterAccessFunctions, GIModelObject, IViewedModelObject
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    GIChoiceContainer

    @NotThreadSafe
 @PublishedApi(value=ADDITIONS_ALLOWED)
public interface GIContainer
extends GIHasContainer
    Base interface of bswmd model container.

    All method parameters must be non-null unless documented otherwise.
